# ============================================================
# Chaos Simulator — Vercel-only deployment
# ============================================================
# No environment variables are required for deployment!
# All state lives in a module-level singleton inside the
# Next.js serverless function.
#
# Optional: enable Vercel KV (Redis) for cross-instance state
# persistence. Without KV, state resets on cold starts.
#
#   KV_REST_API_URL=
#   KV_REST_API_TOKEN=
# ============================================================
